eryWidget\" data-widget-id=\"4ca2ed65-717e-4e67-bbb5-6578b8c6acac\" class=\"colored-block__title\">\n        \n\n\n\n        \n        <h2 id=\"sec-terms\" style=\"display: inline-block\" class=\"section__title left-bordered-title\">Index Terms</h2><span> (auto-classified)</span>\n\n        </div>\n    \n\n<ol class=\"rlist organizational-chart\"><li><h6>Experiences with professional theatre for awareness raising</h6><ol class=\"rlist level-1  ch-1\"><li><div data-background=\"#808080\" style=\"background-color:#808080;box-shadow:none\"><p><a href=\"/topic/ccs2012/10003120?SeriesKey=iwc&amp;expand=all\">Human-centered computing</a></p></div><ol class=\"rlist level-2 ch-2 hasNodes\"><li><div data-background=\"#F5F5F5\" style=\"background-color:#F5F5F5;box-shadow:none\"><p><a href=\"/topic/ccs2012/10003120.10003121?SeriesKey=iwc&amp;expand=all\">Human computer interaction (HCI)</a></p></div><ol class=\"rlist level-3 ch-0\"></ol></li><li><div data-background=\"#808080\" style=\"background-color:#808080;box-shadow:none\"><p><a href=\"/topic/ccs2012/10003120.10003123?SeriesKey=iwc&amp;expand=all\">Interaction design</a></p></div><ol class=\"rlist level-4 ch-1 hasNodes\"><li><div data-background=\"#808080\" style=\"background-color:#808080;box-shadow:none\"><p><a href=\"/topic/ccs2012/10003120.10003123.10010860?SeriesKey=iwc&amp;expand=all\">Interaction design process and methods</a></p></div><ol class=\"rlist level-5 ch-1 hasNodes\"><li><div data-background=\"#808080\" style=\"background-color:#808080;box-shadow:none\"><p><a href=\"/topic/ccs2012/10003120.10003123.10010860.10010859?SeriesKey=iwc&amp;expand=all\">User centered design</a></p></div><ol class=\"rlist level-6 ch-0\"></ol></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol>\n\n        </div>\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n        <div data-widget-def=\"graphQueryWidget\" data-widget-id=\"91639479-279a-46e3-b7c7-f902a3fd7945\" class=\"toc__section accordion-tabbed__tab\">\n        \n\n\n\n        \n        \n\n\n\n\n